						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment of a thousand <hi rend="italic">kuḻi</hi> and odd of land made by one Ālālasundara-Vēḷaikkāṟaṉ of Tiruvaṇṇāmalai, for the maintenance of a well constructed by a <hi rend="italic">kaikkōḷa</hi> named Āyiramārāyaṉ of Eyil and for the requirements of worship to the image Vēṅgai-Vināyaka.</p>						

